{"id":"pattern-example-001","type":"pattern","fact":"Example: Use mock factories for all test data instead of manual mock objects with 'as Type' assertions.","recommendation":"Create centralized mock factory functions (createMockUser, createMockOrg, etc.) and import them in tests.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"documentation","reference":"Testing guide","date":"2026-01-09"}],"tags":["testing","mocks","factories"],"affectedFiles":["**/*.test.ts"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-01-09T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-01-09T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
{"id":"pattern-empty-vue-stubs","type":"pattern","fact":"When creating router entries that lazy-load pages not yet implemented, use empty stubs with only <template><div /></template> and no <script> block. Stubs with script code register as 0% coverage.","recommendation":"Create minimal template-only stubs for pages referenced by router but built in later tasks. Replace with full implementation when the task is reached.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"agent","reference":"Issue #16 coverage gate failure","date":"2026-04-12"}],"tags":["vue","coverage","router","stubs","parallel-tasks"],"affectedFiles":["packages/client/src/pages/**/*.vue"],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-04-12T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
{"id":"pattern-subagent-tdd-incomplete","type":"pattern","fact":"Coding subagents frequently complete only the TDD red phase (test files) before hitting context limits, leaving implementation unwritten.","recommendation":"After subagent completion, always verify both test AND implementation files exist. Be prepared to implement from the test spec when the agent only produced tests.","confidence":"high","provenance":[{"source":"agent","reference":"Issue #17 orchestrated execution — WU-004/005 and WU-006/007 agents","date":"2026-04-12"}],"tags":["orchestration","subagents","tdd","context-limits"],"affectedFiles":[],"affectedServices":[],"createdAt":"2026-04-12T00:00:00Z","updatedAt":"2026-04-12T00:00:00Z","usageCount":0,"helpfulCount":0,"outdatedReports":0}
